1) Start MAMP/WAMP

2) Open mysql CLI (type mysql in terminal) and execute following commands in the correct order:
    * CREATE USER 'webadmin'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'webadmin';
    * GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO 'webadmin'@'localhost';
    * CREATE DATABASE webproject;
    * use webproject;
    * CREATE TABLE `presentations` ( `id` INTEGER NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `data` text NOT NULL, `tags` varchar(256) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci;
    * INSERT INTO `presentations` (`name`, `tags`, `data`) VALUES ('HTML', 'beginner, security', '=slide\r\n p \'Test\'');

3) ACCESS: http://localhost:8888/index.php